            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
              Commercial Real Estate
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Specialized expertise in commercial properties, investment
              opportunities, and business real estate transactions.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Office & retail spaces</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Investment properties</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Commercial leasing</span>
